@mistermoyal Bonjour moyal,
Nous vous prions de nous indiquer votre numéro de réclamation et votre email afin que nous puissions vérifier cette situation. Nous vous recommandons de le faire par message privé pour des raisons de confidentialité. 
Merci

@Maggie247 @maggie247 Hello, you may verify the charges for excess checked baggage weight accessing the following link: https://t.co/xMcImo65oG
We also inform that excess baggage weight is charged directly at the airport. If you have additional questions, please let us know. 
Thank you.

@marcnoruega @marcnoruega Hello MARK,
We replied by direct message.
Thank you.

@thomasmat92 Hello,
Please let us know the ticket numbers so that we can check this situation. We recommend that you do so by private message due to confidentiality reasons.
Thank you

@Sharon03046627 Hello Sharon,
We understand your dissatisfaction and apologize for the delay in finalizing your case. However, we would like to assure you that your case is not forgotten and you will be contacted by email as soon as possible regarding this matter.
Thank you

@obussti Hello muhamad,
We regret this situation and apologize for any inconvenience. In order to verify your case, please let us know your lost baggage claim number (PIR). We recommend that you do so by private message due to confidentiality reasons.
Thank you

@dadrail @dadrail Hello Dad Rail, can you inform us if you already submitted the complaint? Can you indicate us the complaint number? 
For confidential reasons we suggest that you send it by direct message. 
Thank you.

@mormubis Hello Adrián,
We have answered your private message and remain available to assist you.
Thank you.

@HevMM01 Hello Heather,
We have answered your private message and remain available to assist you.
Thank you.

@iurifarenzena Iuri,
Já respondemos à sua DM.
Informamos que poderá efetuar a sua reserva online sem efetuar Login de cliente.

@pjmlantunes Hello Paulo,
we sincerely apologise for the delay on your case's resolution. We assure you nonetheless all efforts are being made so the situation can be analysed and you can receive feedback, by email, as briefly as possible.
Thank you.

@DamianWestwood Hello Damian,
we have replied by DM.
Thank you.

@jeepsfort144 Hi Jean-Philippe,
we are truly sorry for the situation and for all inconvenience it is causing you. To verify, please confirm us your booking code/ticket number and your lost luggage file reference (PIR). For confidentiality reasons, we suggest sending the data by DM.
Thank you.

@jo_bartontaylor Hello Jo, 
We have answered your private message and remain available to assist you.
Thank you.

@juanma_dopiera @BlancaPlanet @PatoBke Hola Juanma,
hemos respondido por DM.
Gracias.

@justinestrand1 (2/2)
- the passenger's first and last name and date of birth;  
- phone number and email address;  
- type of fare desired (https://t.co/NUL9auuEII).  
For security reasons, we suggest you to send it by DM. 
Thank you!

@justinestrand1 Hello Justine,
We apologize for the reported situation.
If you would like to proceed with the booking, please provide us with the following information:  
- desired date and route;  
(1/2)

@rusyasurkova Hello masha,
